{"snp5.1:0.1":"Sutta Nipata 5.1 ","snp5.1:0.2":"Vatthugatha ","snp5.1:1.1":"Kosalanam pura ramma, ","snp5.1:1.2":"agama dakkhinapatham; ","snp5.1:1.3":"Akincannam patthayano, ","snp5.1:1.4":"brahmano mantaparagu. ","snp5.1:2.1":"So assakassa visaye, ","snp5.1:2.2":"alakassa samasane; ","snp5.1:2.3":"Vasi godhavarikule, ","snp5.1:2.4":"unchena ca phalena ca. ","snp5.1:3.1":"Tasseva upanissaya, ","snp5.1:3.2":"gamo ca vipulo ahu; ","snp5.1:3.3":"Tato jatena ayena, ","snp5.1:3.4":"mahayannamakappayi. ","snp5.1:4.1":"Mahayannam yajitvana, ","snp5.1:4.2":"puna pavisi assamam; ","snp5.1:4.3":"Tasmim patipavitthamhi, ","snp5.1:4.4":"anno aganchi brahmano. ","snp5.1:5.1":"Ugghattapado tasito, ","snp5.1:5.2":"pankadanto rajassiro; ","snp5.1:5.3":"So ca nam upasankamma, ","snp5.1:5.4":"satani panca yacati. ","snp5.1:6.1":"Tamenam bavari disva, ","snp5.1:6.2":"asanena nimantayi; ","snp5.1:6.3":"Sukhanca kusalam pucchi, ","snp5.1:6.4":"idam vacanamabravi. ","snp5.1:7.1":"“Yam kho mama deyyadhammam, ","snp5.1:7.2":"Sabbam visajjitam maya; ","snp5.1:7.3":"Anujanahi me brahme, ","snp5.1:7.4":"Natthi pancasatani me”. ","snp5.1:8.1":"“Sace me yacamanassa, ","snp5.1:8.2":"bhavam nanupadassati; ","snp5.1:8.3":"Sattame divase tuyham, ","snp5.1:8.4":"muddha phalatu sattadha”. ","snp5.1:9.1":"Abhisankharitva kuhako, ","snp5.1:9.2":"bheravam so akittayi; ","snp5.1:9.3":"Tassa tam vacanam sutva, ","snp5.1:9.4":"bavari dukkhito ahu. ","snp5.1:10.1":"Ussussati anaharo, ","snp5.1:10.2":"Sokasallasamappito; ","snp5.1:10.3":"Athopi evam cittassa, ","snp5.1:10.4":"Jhane na ramati mano. ","snp5.1:11.1":"Utrastam dukkhitam disva, ","snp5.1:11.2":"Devata atthakamini; ","snp5.1:11.3":"Bavarim upasankamma, ","snp5.1:11.4":"Idam vacanamabravi. ","snp5.1:12.1":"“Na so muddham pajanati, ","snp5.1:12.2":"Kuhako so dhanatthiko; ","snp5.1:12.3":"Muddhani muddhapate va, ","snp5.1:12.4":"Nanam tassa na vijjati”. ","snp5.1:13.1":"“Bhoti carahi janasi, ","snp5.1:13.2":"Tam me akkhahi pucchita; ","snp5.1:13.3":"Muddham muddhadhipatanca, ","snp5.1:13.4":"Tam sunoma vaco tava”. ","snp5.1:14.1":"“Ahampetam na janami, ","snp5.1:14.2":"Nanamettha na vijjati; ","snp5.1:14.3":"Muddhani muddhadhipate ca, ","snp5.1:14.4":"Jinanam hettha dassanam”. ","snp5.1:15.1":"“Atha ko carahi janati, ","snp5.1:15.2":"Asmim pathavimandale; ","snp5.1:15.3":"Muddham muddhadhipatanca, ","snp5.1:15.4":"Tam me akkhahi devate”. ","snp5.1:16.1":"“Pura kapilavatthumha, ","snp5.1:16.2":"Nikkhanto lokanayako; ","snp5.1:16.3":"Apacco okkakarajassa, ","snp5.1:16.4":"Sakyaputto pabhankaro. ","snp5.1:17.1":"So hi brahmana sambuddho, ","snp5.1:17.2":"Sabbadhammana paragu; ","snp5.1:17.3":"Sabbabhinnabalappatto, ","snp5.1:17.4":"Sabbadhammesu cakkhuma; ","snp5.1:17.5":"Sabbakammakkhayam patto, ","snp5.1:17.6":"Vimutto upadhikkhaye. ","snp5.1:18.1":"Buddho so bhagava loke, ","snp5.1:18.2":"Dhammam deseti cakkhuma; ","snp5.1:18.3":"Tam tvam gantvana pucchassu, ","snp5.1:18.4":"So te tam byakarissati”. ","snp5.1:19.1":"Sambuddhoti vaco sutva, ","snp5.1:19.2":"Udaggo bavari ahu; ","snp5.1:19.3":"Sokassa tanuko asi, ","snp5.1:19.4":"Pitinca vipulam labhi. ","snp5.1:20.1":"So bavari attamano udaggo, ","snp5.1:20.2":"Tam devatam pucchati vedajato; ","snp5.1:20.3":"“Katamamhi game nigamamhi va pana, ","snp5.1:20.4":"Katamamhi va janapade lokanatho; ","snp5.1:20.5":"Yattha gantvana passemu, ","snp5.1:20.6":"Sambuddham dvipaduttamam”. ","snp5.1:21.1":"“Savatthiyam kosalamandire jino, ","snp5.1:21.2":"Pahutapanno varabhurimedhaso; ","snp5.1:21.3":"So sakyaputto vidhuro anasavo, ","snp5.1:21.4":"Muddhadhipatassa vidu narasabho”. ","snp5.1:22.1":"Tato amantayi sisse, ","snp5.1:22.2":"Brahmane mantaparage; ","snp5.1:22.3":"“Etha manava akkhissam, ","snp5.1:22.4":"Sunatha vacanam mama. ","snp5.1:23.1":"Yasseso dullabho loke, ","snp5.1:23.2":"Patubhavo abhinhaso; ","snp5.1:23.3":"Svajja lokamhi uppanno, ","snp5.1:23.4":"Sambuddho iti vissuto; ","snp5.1:23.5":"Khippam gantvana savatthim, ","snp5.1:23.6":"Passavho dvipaduttamam”. ","snp5.1:24.1":"“Katham carahi janemu, ","snp5.1:24.2":"Disva buddhoti brahmana; ","snp5.1:24.3":"Ajanatam no pabruhi, ","snp5.1:24.4":"Yatha janemu tam mayam”. ","snp5.1:25.1":"“Agatani hi mantesu, ","snp5.1:25.2":"Mahapurisalakkhana; ","snp5.1:25.3":"Dvattimsani ca byakkhata, ","snp5.1:25.4":"Samatta anupubbaso. ","snp5.1:26.1":"Yassete honti gattesu, ","snp5.1:26.2":"Mahapurisalakkhana; ","snp5.1:26.3":"Dveyeva tassa gatiyo, ","snp5.1:26.4":"Tatiya hi na vijjati. ","snp5.1:27.1":"Sace agaram avasati, ","snp5.1:27.2":"Vijeyya pathavim imam; ","snp5.1:27.3":"Adandena asatthena, ","snp5.1:27.4":"Dhammena manusasati. ","snp5.1:28.1":"Sace ca so pabbajati, ","snp5.1:28.2":"Agara anagariyam; ","snp5.1:28.3":"Vivattacchado sambuddho, ","snp5.1:28.4":"Araha bhavati anuttaro. ","snp5.1:29.1":"Jatim gottanca lakkhanam, ","snp5.1:29.2":"Mante sisse punapare; ","snp5.1:29.3":"Muddham muddhadhipatanca, ","snp5.1:29.4":"Manasayeva pucchatha. ","snp5.1:30.1":"Anavaranadassavi, ","snp5.1:30.2":"Yadi buddho bhavissati; ","snp5.1:30.3":"Manasa pucchite panhe, ","snp5.1:30.4":"Vacaya vissajessati”. ","snp5.1:31.1":"Bavarissa vaco sutva, ","snp5.1:31.2":"Sissa solasa brahmana; ","snp5.1:31.3":"Ajito tissametteyyo, ","snp5.1:31.4":"Punnako atha mettagu. ","snp5.1:32.1":"Dhotako upasivo ca, ","snp5.1:32.2":"Nando ca atha hemako; ","snp5.1:32.3":"Todeyya-kappa dubhayo, ","snp5.1:32.4":"Jatukanni ca pandito. ","snp5.1:33.1":"Bhadravudho udayo ca, ","snp5.1:33.2":"Posalo capi brahmano; ","snp5.1:33.3":"Mogharaja ca medhavi, ","snp5.1:33.4":"Pingiyo ca mahaisi. ","snp5.1:34.1":"Paccekaganino sabbe, ","snp5.1:34.2":"Sabbalokassa vissuta; ","snp5.1:34.3":"Jhayi jhanarata dhira, ","snp5.1:34.4":"Pubbavasanavasita. ","snp5.1:35.1":"Bavarim abhivadetva, ","snp5.1:35.2":"Katva ca nam padakkhinam; ","snp5.1:35.3":"Jatajinadhara sabbe, ","snp5.1:35.4":"Pakkamum uttaramukha. ","snp5.1:36.1":"Alakassa patitthanam, ","snp5.1:36.2":"Purimahissatim tada; ","snp5.1:36.3":"Ujjenincapi gonaddham, ","snp5.1:36.4":"Vedisam vanasavhayam. ","snp5.1:37.1":"Kosambincapi saketam, ","snp5.1:37.2":"Savatthinca puruttamam; ","snp5.1:37.3":"Setabyam kapilavatthum, ","snp5.1:37.4":"Kusinaranca mandiram. ","snp5.1:38.1":"Pavanca bhoganagaram, ","snp5.1:38.2":"Vesalim magadham puram; ","snp5.1:38.3":"Pasanakam cetiyanca, ","snp5.1:38.4":"Ramaniyam manoramam. ","snp5.1:39.1":"Tasitovudakam sitam, ","snp5.1:39.2":"Mahalabhamva vanijo; ","snp5.1:39.3":"Chayam ghammabhitattova, ","snp5.1:39.4":"Turita pabbatamaruhum. ","snp5.1:40.1":"Bhagava tamhi samaye, ","snp5.1:40.2":"Bhikkhusanghapurakkhato; ","snp5.1:40.3":"Bhikkhunam dhammam deseti, ","snp5.1:40.4":"Sihova nadati vane. ","snp5.1:41.1":"Ajito addasa buddham, ","snp5.1:41.2":"Sataramsimva bhanumam; ","snp5.1:41.3":"Candam yatha pannarase, ","snp5.1:41.4":"Paripurim upagatam. ","snp5.1:42.1":"Athassa gatte disvana, ","snp5.1:42.2":"Paripuranca byanjanam; ","snp5.1:42.3":"Ekamantam thito hattho, ","snp5.1:42.4":"Manopanhe apucchatha. ","snp5.1:43.1":"“Adissa jammanam bruhi, ","snp5.1:43.2":"Gottam bruhi salakkhanam; ","snp5.1:43.3":"Mantesu paramim bruhi, ","snp5.1:43.4":"Kati vaceti brahmano”. ","snp5.1:44.1":"“Visam vassasatam ayu, ","snp5.1:44.2":"So ca gottena bavari; ","snp5.1:44.3":"Tinissa lakkhana gatte, ","snp5.1:44.4":"Tinnam vedana paragu. ","snp5.1:45.1":"Lakkhane itihase ca, ","snp5.1:45.2":"Sanighandusaketubhe; ","snp5.1:45.3":"Pancasatani vaceti, ","snp5.1:45.4":"Sadhamme paramim gato”. ","snp5.1:46.1":"“Lakkhananam pavicayam, ","snp5.1:46.2":"Bavarissa naruttama; ","snp5.1:46.3":"Kankhacchida pakasehi, ","snp5.1:46.4":"Ma no kankhayitam ahu”. ","snp5.1:47.1":"“Mukham jivhaya chadeti, ","snp5.1:47.2":"Unnassa bhamukantare; ","snp5.1:47.3":"Kosohitam vatthaguyham, ","snp5.1:47.4":"Evam janahi manava”. ","snp5.1:48.1":"Pucchanhi kinci asunanto, ","snp5.1:48.2":"Sutva panhe viyakate; ","snp5.1:48.3":"Vicinteti jano sabbo, ","snp5.1:48.4":"Vedajato katanjali. ","snp5.1:49.1":"“Ko nu devo va brahma va, ","snp5.1:49.2":"Indo vapi sujampati; ","snp5.1:49.3":"Manasa pucchite panhe, ","snp5.1:49.4":"Kametam patibhasati”. ","snp5.1:50.1":"“Muddham muddhadhipatanca, ","snp5.1:50.2":"Bavari paripucchati; ","snp5.1:50.3":"Tam byakarohi bhagava, ","snp5.1:50.4":"Kankham vinaya no ise”. ","snp5.1:51.1":"“Avijja muddhati janahi, ","snp5.1:51.2":"Vijja muddhadhipatini; ","snp5.1:51.3":"Saddhasatisamadhihi, ","snp5.1:51.4":"Chandaviriyena samyuta”. ","snp5.1:52.1":"Tato vedena mahata, ","snp5.1:52.2":"Santhambhitvana manavo; ","snp5.1:52.3":"Ekamsam ajinam katva, ","snp5.1:52.4":"Padesu sirasa pati. ","snp5.1:53.1":"“Bavari brahmano bhoto, ","snp5.1:53.2":"Saha sissehi marisa; ","snp5.1:53.3":"Udaggacitto sumano, ","snp5.1:53.4":"Pade vandati cakkhuma”. ","snp5.1:54.1":"“Sukhito bavari hotu, ","snp5.1:54.2":"Saha sissehi brahmano; ","snp5.1:54.3":"Tvancapi sukhito hohi, ","snp5.1:54.4":"Ciram jivahi manava. ","snp5.1:55.1":"Bavarissa ca tuyham va, ","snp5.1:55.2":"Sabbesam sabbasamsayam; ","snp5.1:55.3":"Katavakasa pucchavho, ","snp5.1:55.4":"Yam kinci manasicchatha”. ","snp5.1:56.1":"Sambuddhena katokaso, ","snp5.1:56.2":"Nisiditvana panjali; ","snp5.1:56.3":"Ajito pathamam panham, ","snp5.1:56.4":"Tattha pucchi tathagatam. ","snp5.1:56.5":"Vatthugatha nitthita. "}